ums Chart|UK]]<br><ref name=\"UK\">Peak chart positions in the United Kingdom:\n* All except noted: {{cite web |url=https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/23332/killers/ |title=The Killers |publisher=[[Official Charts Company]] |accessdate=February 28, 2016}}\n* \"Shadowplay\", \"A Dustland Fairytale\" and \"\u00a1Happy Birthday Guadalupe!\": {{cite web |url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/CLUK_K.HTM |title=Chart Log UK (1994\u20132010): Alex K \u2013 Kyuss |website=Zobbel |accessdate=February 28, 2016}}\n* \"The Cowboys' Christmas Ball\": {{cite web |url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/CLUK2011.HTM |title=Chart Log UK \u2013 Weekly Updates Sales 2011 |website=Zobbel |accessdate=February 28, 2016}}\n* \"Joel the Lump of Coal\": {{cite web |url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/141213cluk.txt |title=CHART: CLUK Update 13.12.2014 (wk49) |website=Zobbel |accessdate=February 28, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Hot Fuss]]''\n|\n* Released: June 15, 2004\n* Label: [[Island Records|Island]]\n* Formats: [[Compact disc|CD]], [[LP record|LP]], [[Music download|download]]\n| 7 || 1 || 95 || 4 || 75 || 1 || 46 || 5 || 48 || 1\n|\n* World: 7,000,000<ref name=\"sfweekly\">{{cite web |last=Alexandra |first=Rae |url=https://archives.sfweekly.com/sanfrancisco/hate-the-killers-heres-why-you-shouldnt/Content?oid=2187270 |title=Hate the Killers? Here's Why You Shouldn't |work=[[SF Weekly]] |date=December 5, 2012 |accessdate=March 28, 2020}}</ref>\n* US: 3,750,000<ref>{{cite web |last=Caulfield |first=Keith |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7669825/billboard-200-chart-moves-3-doors-down-toby-keith-trump |title=Billboard 200 Chart Moves: 3 Doors Down & Toby Keith Return After Trump Inauguration Concert |work=Billboard |date=January 26, 2017 |accessdate=July 2, 2017}}</ref>\n* UK: 2,244,150<ref name=\"UK-sales-2018\">{{cite web |last=Hanley |first=James |url=https://www.musicweek.com/talent/read/mr-brightside-has-become-an-anthem-for-a-generation-the-killers-on-the-indie-classi