rs-celebrate-sams-town-anniversary-with-vegas-extravaganza-vinyl-reissue/ |title=The Killers Celebrate 'Sam's Town' Anniversary With Vegas Extravaganza, Vinyl Reissue |work=[[Forbes]] |date=August 31, 2016 |accessdate=October 12, 2018}}</ref>\n* US: 1,300,000<ref>{{cite web |last=Peters |first=Mitchell |url=https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/1305701/umg-merch-arm-inks-deal-with-the-killers |title=UMG Merch Arm Inks Deal With The Killers |work=Billboard |date=July 23, 2008 |accessdate=February 28, 2016}}</ref>\n* UK: 1,528,003<ref name=\"UK-sales-2017\">{{cite web |last=Stassen |first=Murray |url=https://www.musicweek.com/labels/read/virgin-emi-vows-to-deliver-fifth-no-1-for-the-killers/069031 |title=Virgin EMI vows to deliver fifth No.1 for The Killers |work=Music Week |date=July 4, 2017 |accessdate=July 4, 2017 |url-access=subscription}}</ref>\n|\n* RIAA: Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/>\n* ARIA: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"ARIA-albums-2007\">{{cite certification|region=Australia|type=album|certyear=2007|accessdate=February 4, 2011}}</ref>\n* BEA: Gold<ref name=\"BEA-2007\"/>\n* BPI: 5\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* BVMI: Gold<ref name=\"BVMI\"/>\n* [[Irish Recorded Music Association|IRMA]]: 4\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite certification|region=Ireland|award=Platinum|number=4|certyear=2006|accessdate=January 6, 2012}}</ref>\n* MC: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"MC\"/>\n* RMNZ: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"radioscope-albums\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Day & Age]]''\n|\n* Released: November 18, 2008\n* Label: Island\n* Formats: CD, LP, download\n| 6 || 4 || 12 || 6 || 8 || 1 || 12 || 2 || 4 || 1\n|\n* World: 3,000,000<ref>{{cite web |last=Hunt |first=Chase |url=http://www.axs.com/brandon-flowers-of-the-killers-confident-band-will-record-another-albu-52759 |title=Brandon Flowers of The Killers confident band will record another album |publisher=[[AXS (ticket merchant)|AXS]] |date=May 9, 2015 |accessdate=February 28, 2016}}</ref>\n* US: 774,000<ref>{{cite web |last