ers Chart History: Rock Digital Song Sales |work=Billboard |accessdate=April 25, 2018}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Ultratop#Ultratip|BEL<br>Tip<br>(FL)]]<br><ref name=\"BEL-(FL)\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zobbel.de/cluk/CLUK2012.HTM |title=Chart Log UK \u2013 2012 + Weekly Updates + Sales 2012 |website=Zobbel |accessdate=February 28, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Flesh and Bone\"\n| 2012\n| 17 || 38 || \u2014 || 184\n| ''Battle Born''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Tyson vs Douglas\"\n| 2017\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || 39 || \u2014\n| ''Wonderful Wonderful''\n|}\n\n==Guest appearances==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|+ List of non-single guest appearances, showing year released and album name\n! scope=\"col\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Move Away\"\n| 2007\n| ''[[Spider-Man 3 (soundtrack)|Music from and Inspired by Spider-Man 3]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Hotel California]]\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2009\n| ''[[Rhythms del Mundo Classics]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"A White Demon Love Song\"\n| ''[[The Twilight Saga: New Moon (soundtrack)|The Twilight Saga: New Moon (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack)]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Spaceship Adventure\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2011\n| ''[[Yo Gabba Gabba!#Soundtrack releases|Yo Gabba Gabba! Music Is... Awesome! Vol. 3]]''<ref>{{cite web |last=Kellman |first=Andy |url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/music-isawesome!-vol-3-mw0002187952 |title=Music Is...Awesome!, Vol. 3 \u2013 Yo Gabba Gabba! |website=[[AllMusic]] |accessdate=February 28, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Ultraviolet (Light My Way)]]\"\n| ''[[AHK-toong BAY-bi Covered]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Mona Lisas and Mad Hatters]]\"\n| 2018\n| ''[[Revamp & Restoration#Revamp|Revamp: Reimagining the Songs of Elton John & Bernie Taupin]]''\n|}\n\n==Videography==